data.description: Welcome to this charming updated home located in the desirable Countryside development of Clayton, New Jersey. This lovely property features 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 modern bathrooms, and a large yard perfect for relaxing and entertaining. Some highlights of 409 Moore Blvd include: - Four generously sized bedrooms, including a master suite with a walk-in closet and master bathroom - Three elegantly updated bathrooms with contemporary fixtures - A beautifully maintained yard with an outdoor fire pit and brand-new deck for enjoying the outdoors This home has been recently remodeled with high-quality materials, creating a modern and comfortable living space. The open floor plan connecting the living room, dining area, and kitchen is ideal for hosting guests or simply enjoying everyday life. Come see all that this beautiful residence has to offer - you won't be disappointed!  Welcome to 409 Moore Blvd!
